OL,3,CScotland's controversial new hate
OL,4,Ccrime laws come into force
OL,6,FBut the legislation has raised
OL,7,Fconcerns about a potential chilling of
OL,8,Ffree speech.
OL,10,FProminent critics include author JK
OL,11,FRowling, podcaster Joe Rogan and Elon
OL,12,FMusk, the owner of X - formerly
OL,13,FTwitter.
