OL,3,CScotland's controversial new hate
OL,4,Ccrime laws come into force
OL,6,FThis includes an explicit clause, a
OL,7,Fdefence for the accused's behaviour
OL,8,Fbeing "reasonable" and that the Act is
OL,9,Fcompatible with the European
OL,10,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,12,FMr Yousaf also told journalists on
OL,13,FFriday that the legislation would not
OL,14,Fgo the way of other high-profile
OL,15,Flegislative U-turns under the SNP,
OL,16,Fsuch as the named persons scheme and
OL,17,Fthe Offensive Behaviour at Football
OL,18,FAct.
